en_354059_0	Brigadier Deepal Wanniarachchi of Sri Lanka Signal Corps (SLSC) assumed office as the 4th Director of the Directorate of Quality Assurance this morning (4) at the Army Headquarters.
en_354059_1	He symbolized the acceptance of office by leaving his signature for an official document amid religious observances.
en_354059_2	Staff Officers of the Directorate and Other Ranks were at the venue.
en_354059_3	He was the Commandant at the Army Logistic School at Trincomalee before this appointment.
